message:

title: Made camera able to record videos. Added a FPS control.
message:
Made camera able to record videos. Added a FPS control.

Even though the FPS control is added, it’s by all means a suggestion
ergo it doesn’t produce the result you expect most of the time.

title: Added the option of saving sensor data to file.
message:
Added the option of saving sensor data to file.

It works like a charm, howbeit there is a bug with the selection part.
Therefore it must be debugged so that we can select where to save our
data.
